ēṣāmahaṅ samuddhartā mṛtyusaṅsārasāgarāt.<br><br>bhavāmi nacirātpārtha mayyāvēśitacētasām৷৷12.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2564,14,'rajō rāgātmakaṅ viddhi tṛṣṇāsaṅgasamudbhavam.<br><br>tannibadhnāti kauntēya karmasaṅgēna dēhinam৷৷14.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2565,11,'ihaikasthaṅ jagatkṛtsnaṅ paśyādya sacarācaram.<br><br>mama dēhē guḍākēśa yaccānyaddraṣṭumicchasi৷৷11.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2566,4,'yadā yadā hi dharmasya glānirbhavati bhārata.<br><br>abhyutthānamadharmasya tadā৷৷tmānaṅ sṛjāmyaham৷৷4.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2567,13,'icchā dvēṣaḥ sukhaṅ duḥkhaṅ saṅghātaścētanādhṛtiḥ.<br><br>ētatkṣētraṅ samāsēna savikāramudāhṛtam৷৷13.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2568,7,'mattaḥ parataraṅ nānyatkiñcidasti dhanañjaya.<br><br>mayi sarvamidaṅ prōtaṅ sūtrē maṇigaṇā iva৷৷7.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2569,6,'jitātmanaḥ praśāntasya paramātmā samāhitaḥ.<br><br>śītōṣṇasukhaduḥkhēṣu tathā mānāpamānayōḥ৷৷6.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2570,10,'ētāṅ vibhūtiṅ yōgaṅ ca mama yō vētti tattvataḥ.<br><br>sō.vikampēna yōgēna yujyatē nātra saṅśayaḥ৷৷10.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2571,16,'pravṛttiṅ ca nivṛttiṅ ca janā na vidurāsurāḥ.<br><br>na śaucaṅ nāpi cācārō na satyaṅ tēṣu vidyatē৷৷16.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2572,1,'asmākaṅ tu viśiṣṭā yē tānnibōdha dvijōttama.<br><br>nāyakā mama sainyasya saṅjñārthaṅ tānbravīmi tē৷৷1.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2573,15,'mamaivāṅśō jīvalōkē jīvabhūtaḥ sanātanaḥ.<br><br>manaḥṣaṣṭhānīndriyāṇi prakṛtisthāni karṣati৷৷15.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2574,3,'yastvindriyāṇi manasā niyamyārabhatē.rjuna.<br><br>karmēndriyaiḥ karmayōgamasaktaḥ sa viśiṣyatē৷৷3.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2575,8,'tasmātsarvēṣu kālēṣu māmanusmara yudhya ca.<br><br>mayyarpitamanōbuddhirmāmēvaiṣyasyasaṅśayam৷৷8.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2576,9,'sarvabhūtāni kauntēya prakṛtiṅ yānti māmikām.<br><br>kalpakṣayē punastāni kalpādau visṛjāmyaham৷৷9.7৷৷<br><br>','ro','Roman',7),(2577,18,'niyatasya tu saṅnyāsaḥ karmaṇō nōpapadyatē.<br><br>mōhāttasya parityā